            <title>[LU-14818] DoM: rework sanity-flr test_6 to check DOM+FLR use cases</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14818</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-flr.sh test_6 was introduced along with initial FLR implementation which didn&apos;t work with DoM. Test was checking that DOM+FLR striping causes error. Now DoM+FLR is possible combination and test do nothing, it passes because still causes errors as expected but these errors are due to wrong &lt;tt&gt;lfs&lt;/tt&gt; syntax.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test should be reworked to check valid and invalid combinations of DOM+FLR&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
